aking them EXPLICIT as datoms enables: (1) F(S) delta display, (2) accurate M(t) from turn 1, (3) provable cross-session monotonic convergence, (4) session quality metrics (convergence rate = dF/dt), (5) trajectory-aware seed context. The session lifecycle forms an adjunction: seed (unit) and harvest (counit) with the session monad completing the algebra. ALGEBRAIC STRUCTURE: Agent attention ⊣ Store state adjunction. Unit = seed (inject store → agent). Counit = harvest (extract agent → store). Session = the natural transformation between them.\nSession entity: :task/t-4a5853fb; Session entity: :task/t-74d6abc0; Session entity: :task/t-5dccaaa1; Session entity: :task/t-8740befa; Session entity: :task/t-ca8a682f; Session entity: :task/t-aff33aa7" :op :assert}
